mudServer.Mobiles
Interface Mobile

All Known Implementing Classes:
Monster, Player
public interface Mobile

Defines methods for which all Mobiles must implement. There are two categories: All methods whose implementation is the same for all Mobiles are implemented by extending MobileStd. All methods whose implementation is dependant on each new class of Mobile are defined here, but implemented in the specific class.

Author:
Nemesis
